author: Red Means Recording
description:
Get these here: https://redmeansrecording.gumroad.com/l/pjrcj
Get my new M8 Drum and Bass album (with bundles) here: https://soundvision.bandcamp.com/album/superstructures

60 synthesizer presets for the Dirtywave M8 tracker focusing on DnB / Jungle bass sound design. From classics to modern, this pack is a slice through the kaleidoscopic world of one of the best genres on the planet.

These are made exclusively with the M8 synthesizer engines, firmware Version 6.0.2A. Make sure you M8 is updated to at least this firmware: https://dirtywave.com/pages/resources-downloads

This pack will be free through September in honor the M8 Discord's Jungle community compilation challenge. Join the Dirtywave M8 Discord to participate.
